column6: So welcome to this interview today. I'm sitting here with Natalie and we're going to have just a little interview with two questions.
My name is Lars and I'm handing over to my interviewee to introduce herself.
Thank you. My name is Natalie. I'm an employee at GAG and we are testing this new device.
Okay; thank you. My first question to you is; when is your next field trip?
That is a good question; Lars. I'm not sure. We are hoping for May.
Okay; you're hoping for May. When was your last field trip?
Okay; thank you very much for the interview.
